NYBP Mug Club Memberships
NYBP Mug Club Memberships
end header
2025 NYBP Mug Club Memberships on sale November 29, 2024!
Welcome to New York Beer Project's most exclusive Membership Program! An NYBP Mug Club Membership is redeemable at ALL FOUR of our existing and future locations. View all of the exclusive membership benefits below:
NYBP Mug Club Membership Benefits Include:
Exclusive Mug Club member merchandise item at sign-up (redeemable at your home base)
Complimentary sign-up beer (on first visit only)
Free birthday beer
Mug Club VIPs receive and upgrade on every beer purchased. If the beer is normally served in a pint glass, VIPs receive the beer in a 20 oz. Mug club mug. High ABV 13 oz. goblet beers get upgraded to a pint, etc.
10% off all NYBP merchandise
20% off entire bill every Tuesday (excludes gift card sales and Mug Club membership sales)
$1 off growler and crowler fills
Free 5 oz. taster pour of each new beer on that beer’s release dat
One ticket to NYBP’s Annual Mug Club Appreciation Bash
The fine print:
A 2025 NYBP Mug Club Membership is $100 (+ tax), and is eligible for use starting November 29, 2024 through December 31, 2025.
BONUS PERK: NYBP MEMBERSHIPS ARE AVAILABLE AT ALL NYBP LOCATIONS: NYBP LOCKPORT, NYBP VICTOR, NYBP ORLANDO,
AND NYBP ORCHARD PARK!
NYBP 2025 Mug Club Membership
$100.00
